## What I've learned in the Frontend Masters Gatsby Course


👨🏻‍🏫 - Learn how to leverage free, open source tools including Gatsby, React, and
  GraphQL to build high-performance websites.

👨🏻‍🏫 - Deliver an excellent experience to your users by providing only critical
  assets on load and prefetching assets for subsequent page loads.

👨🏻‍🏫 - Implement performance best practices, such as the PRPL pattern, lazy
  loading assets, and more.

👨🏻‍🏫 - Learn to build and deploy blazing fast websites in the fraction of time.

👨🏻‍🏫 - Create websites quickly with performance baked in.

👨🏻‍🏫 - Deploy your sites for free in minutes with Netlify.
